videos.description: Texas RB Jerrod Heard runs up the middle for a nine-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Texas strike first with 9-yard TD

videos.description: Chris Warren III takes the handoff 26 yards and sets up Texas at the 50-yard line.
videos.headline: Warren III's 26-yard rush takes Texas to midfield

videos.description: Texas QB Sam Ehlinger completes a pass to Collin Johnson for 23-yards.
videos.headline: Ehlinger connects with Johnson for 23-yard gain

videos.description: Texas head coach Tom Herman talks about how his defense has been the aggressor.
videos.headline: Texas' Herman: 'Our defense has been very aggressive

videos.description: Sam Ehlinger hits Lorenzo Joe for 39-yard gain setting Texas up inside the red zone.
videos.headline: Ehlinger to Joe for 39-yard gain sets up Texas TD

videos.description: Texas RB Jerrod Heard takes ball up the middle for a three-yard touchdown to give Texas a 21-0 lead.
videos.headline: Heard's 2nd rush TD widens gap

videos.description: Texas RB Kyle Porter takes the handoff into the end zone from three yards out for the touchdown giving Texas a 28-0 lead.
videos.headline: Porter rush TD extends blowout

videos.description: Texas CB Holton Hill intercepts Montel Aaron and takes it back to the house for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Hill's pick-six continues Texas' rout

videos.description: Texas RB Chris Warren III drags defenders into end zone for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Warren III bulls his way into the end zone for another Texas TD

videos.headline: San Jose State fumbles kickoff, gives Texas ball in red zone

videos.description: Texas QB Sam Ehlinger hits Armanti Foreman with a one-yard pass for the Texas touchdown.
videos.headline: Ehlinger's short pass to Foreman continues Texas' dominance

videos.headline: Carter's rushing TD is Texas' 6th rush TD of game
